":511200,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[本地籃球] 2018年香港男子甲一組聯賽籃總盃及港籃世盃外討論區 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/493935/page/6?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/493935/page/6?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈 無留意到"},{"pid":"405171be9d294b04db1309649decdc46704f9c27","tid":511200,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依幾年都有睇開本地籃球<br />\n下季最大亮點想睇鄭錦興打東方[img]assets/faces/xm/agree.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n終於有人回[img]assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif[/img] 個時佢點解轉會？</blockquote>發夢聽到人講話東方某高層唔鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然唔知內情，但東方俾人感覺都係無咩人情味個種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人情味同內部有問題應該係真<br />\n同埋佢覺得阿興年紀大，冇潛力，佢搵人replace到咁未唔續佢囉<br />\n好似阿ga咁，上季abl+本地賽主力都唔留低<br />\n但兆榮呢d有潛力既我就覺得佢依家要18-19球季abl先打得返，東方都會全力留佢"},{"pid":"32aa58d091cf86a450694bf0bafbd75bce958939","tid":511200,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依幾年都有睇開本地籃球<br />\n下季最大亮點想睇鄭錦興打東方[img]assets/faces/xm/agree.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n終於有人回[img]assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif[/img] 個時佢點解轉會？</blockquote>發夢聽到人講話東方某高層唔鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然唔知內情，但東方俾人感覺都係無咩人情味個種</blockquote>咁職業球隊嘛，睇你點睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你遲啲睇吓遊協個陣有咩東方舊將就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我淨係知阿興話要去爭標球隊<br />\n但最尾去左遊協我笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad625ac4b6e8dd106484145172211cdada4bd97","tid":511200,"uid":79739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":